      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly vehicle that still has plenty of life left? This car is in fair condition and ready for its next owner! While it shows some honest wear from its years on the road, it remains a reliable choice for getting from A to B. It\u2019s the perfect opportunity to own a solid driver at a great price!",
